description: Returns a list of workflow runtime instance metadata objects for a specific image build version.

parameters.name: imageBuildVersionArn
parameters.description: List all workflow runtime instances for the specified image build version resource ARN.

nested_items.name: requestId
nested_items.description: The request ID that uniquely identifies this request.

nested_items.name: workflowExecutions
nested_items.description: Contains an array of runtime details that represents each time a workflow ran for the requested image build version.

nested_items.name: workflowBuildVersionArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the workflow resource build version that ran.

nested_items.name: workflowExecutionId
nested_items.description: Unique identifier that Image Builder assigns to keep track of runtime resources each time it runs a workflow.

nested_items.name: type
nested_items.description: Indicates what type of workflow that Image Builder ran for this runtime instance of the workflow.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The current runtime status for this workflow.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: The runtime output message from the workflow, if applicable.

nested_items.name: totalStepCount
nested_items.description: The total number of steps in the workflow. This should equal the sum of the step counts for steps that succeeded, were skipped, and failed.

nested_items.name: totalStepsSucceeded
nested_items.description: A runtime count for the number of steps in the workflow that ran successfully.

nested_items.name: totalStepsFailed
nested_items.description: A runtime count for the number of steps in the workflow that failed.

nested_items.name: totalStepsSkipped
nested_items.description: A runtime count for the number of steps in the workflow that were skipped.

nested_items.name: startTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp when the runtime instance of this workflow started.

nested_items.name: endTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp when this runtime instance of the workflow finished.

nested_items.name: parallelGroup
nested_items.description: The name of the test group that included the test workflow resource at runtime.

nested_items.name: imageBuildVersionArn
nested_items.description: The resource ARN of the image build version for which you requested a list of workflow runtime details.

nested_items.name: message
nested_items.description: The output message from the list action, if applicable.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The next token used for paginated responses. When this field isn't empty, there are additional elements that the service hasn't included in this request. Use this token with the next request to retrieve additional objects.
